4. User clicks "Yes" to insert columns
5. 5 columns inserted at row 1 (the OLD header row)
6. Original headers+data shift from row 1 to row 6
7. GetSheetData reads from row 1 → finds nothing
8. "No data found" error
9. User's data is now at row 6+ but header is stuck at row 1
```

